        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pour the <strong>cheezy bean mixture </strong>over the cauliflower, making sure everything's covered</p><p>Cover the dish with<strong> tin foil</strong> and put it in the oven for an initial 15 min or until the cauliflower is tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
