      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 15 min, remove the dish from the oven and discard the tin foil</p><p>Top with the <strong>truffle & crispy onion breadcrumbs</strong> and return it to the oven for a final 8-10 min or until golden – this is your <strong>plant-based truffle cauli cheeze & cannellini bean gratin</strong></p><p>While the gratin is cooking, combine your<strong> cider vinegar </strong>with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
